-No change?
-No change.

229
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:33,952
It'll work if the quality is high.

230
00:17:34,019 --> 00:17:36,422
You're right. That's true.

231
00:17:36,488 --> 00:17:38,223
I think it'll work, too.

232
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:41,060
But in case it doesn't,
let's make a jacket.

233
00:17:41,126 --> 00:17:43,262
As emergency insurance.

234
00:17:43,328 --> 00:17:46,365
If you think that'll work, let's do it.

